# 🏨 VRVS Hotel Booking System

A full-stack hotel booking web application built using **MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express, Node.js, HTML/CSS/JavaScript)**.  
This project allows users to register, login, book rooms, and make payments with a simple and clean UI.

---

## 🚀 Features

- User Registration & Login system
- Secure password hashing using bcrypt
- Room browsing system
- Room booking with check-in and check-out dates
- Payment simulation system
- Booking confirmation page
- User dashboard (view & cancel bookings)
- MongoDB database integration
- REST API backend with Express

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Frontend
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)

### Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- bcryptjs
- cors

